and be an ambassador.

325
00:23:37,680 --> 00:23:38,840
No,

326
00:23:38,920 --> 00:23:41,160
I just want to be somebody's wife.

327
00:23:47,680 --> 00:23:50,280
She's a very good student.

328
00:23:50,360 --> 00:23:53,000
You came here on a scholarship,
didn't you?

329
00:23:53,080 --> 00:23:55,280
It's my grandpa's scholarship.

330
00:23:55,360 --> 00:23:58,800
I mean my family's foundation.

331
00:23:58,880 --> 00:24:01,200
I didn't have to compete for it.

332
00:24:01,280 --> 00:24:03,200
Tomorrow is a holiday.

333
00:24:03,280 --> 00:24:06,520
I'll pick you up
and show you around the city.

334
00:24:10,040 --> 00:24:15,360
Do everything you can
to make Saruj fall in love with Poncheewa.

335
00:24:18,040 --> 00:24:19,480
Mr. Saruj,

336
00:24:19,560 --> 00:24:24,120
