you've ever seen is coming up.

337
00:24:24,200 --> 00:24:26,920
Make sure you watch it.

338
00:25:19,480 --> 00:25:21,000
She's so pretty.

339
00:25:22,160 --> 00:25:24,320
No one can take their eyes off her.

340
00:26:02,160 --> 00:26:03,400
Cheewa.

341
00:26:03,480 --> 00:26:04,840
Cheewa.

342
00:26:04,920 --> 00:26:07,600
Come and sit on my lap.
I'll give you a tip.

343
00:26:09,800 --> 00:26:12,520
- Come on.
- Come here.

344
00:26:14,120 --> 00:26:15,400
Don't be shy.

345
00:26:15,480 --> 00:26:16,720
Do you see this?

346
00:26:16,800 --> 00:26:19,680
I have all this for you.

347
00:26:19,760 --> 00:26:21,560
I'll give you double,

348
00:26:21,640 --> 00:26:24,560
but you must lay your head on my chest.

349
00:26:24,640 --> 00:26:26,960
- Come here.
- Come on.

350
00:26:27,040 --> 00:26:28,480
Come down here.

351
00:26:28,560 --> 00:26:30,480
- Come and get your tip.
- Come on.

352
00:26:30,560 --> 00:26:33,800
Come on. Here's my chest.

353
00:26:35,760 --> 00:26:38,200
Thank you so much, Mr. Nat.

354
00:26:38,280 --> 00:26:41,200
Let me give it to Cheewa.

355
00:26:41,280 --> 00:26:42,280
Hey.

356
00:26:42,360 --> 00:26:43,560
- Cheewa.
- Hey.

357
00:26:51,520 --> 00:26:54,840
All right, let's move on to the next show.

358
00:26:54,920 --> 00:26:57,000
Happy birthday, Mr. Nat.

359
00:27:01,920 --> 00:27:05,520
Mr. Mod, will you join me onstage?

360
00:27:06,560 --> 00:27:08,240
Yes, come up here.

361
00:27:08,320 --> 00:27:09,720
- Come on.
- Go.

362
00:27:09,800 --> 00:27:13,200
- Help me wish Mr. Nat a happy birthday.
- I can do it for you.

363
00:27:13,280 --> 00:27:16,360
Please give
a round of applause for Mr. Mod.

364
00:27:19,560 --> 00:27:21,240
This is your…

365
00:27:21,320 --> 00:27:22,200
Head.

366
00:27:22,280 --> 00:27:23,960
- Yes, and this?
- Shoulder.

367
00:27:24,040 --> 00:27:25,240
- Yes.
- Butt.

368
00:27:25,320 --> 00:27:26,760
