Well then, let's try it.

373
00:27:34,360 --> 00:27:35,760
Head, shoulder, butt.

374
00:27:35,840 --> 00:27:38,440
Head, shoulder, butt.

375
00:27:38,520 --> 00:27:40,440
Head, shoulder, butt.

376
00:27:40,520 --> 00:27:41,960
- Head, shoulder, head--
- There you go.

377
00:27:46,640 --> 00:27:48,800
I've seen something like this before.

378
00:27:48,880 --> 00:27:52,680
It's called slapstick. I love it.

379
00:27:52,760 --> 00:27:54,200
I see.

380
00:27:54,280 --> 00:27:55,800
- My goodness.
- Okay.

381
00:27:56,280 --> 00:27:58,440
Touching a man's butt?

382
00:28:01,640 --> 00:28:04,280
That's the end of the show.

383
00:28:04,360 --> 00:28:06,560
Thank you.

384
00:28:07,120 --> 00:28:08,400
What about me?

385
00:28:08,480 --> 00:28:12,320
Thank you so much, Mr. Mod.
You can go now.

386
00:28:12,400 --> 00:28:14,480
Gosh, I didn't get to touch her butt.

387
00:28:14,560 --> 00:28:16,960
Please bring the birthday cake.

388
00:28:41,160 --> 00:28:42,560
Happy birthday!

389
00:28:45,080 --> 00:28:46,240
There we go.

390
00:29:00,640 --> 00:29:02,640
You're taking Mr. Saruj out,

391
00:29:02,720 --> 00:29:06,120
