and scare him off, all right?

392
00:29:06,200 --> 00:29:08,280
- Okay.
- Mr. Saruj.

393
00:29:11,800 --> 00:29:14,240
Take him out for a meal
and listen to some music

394
00:29:14,320 --> 00:29:16,080
somewhere romantic.

395
00:29:16,160 --> 00:29:19,240
Don't take him anywhere weird
or he'll be shocked.

396
00:29:19,320 --> 00:29:20,440
Yes, Mom.

397
00:29:39,880 --> 00:29:41,160
I'm sorry.

398
00:29:41,640 --> 00:29:43,160
It's fine.

399
00:29:44,200 --> 00:29:47,680
You smell so good.

400
00:29:56,120 --> 00:29:59,560
Next time, take him skiing at Jungfrau.

401
00:30:02,120 --> 00:30:03,880
Are you avoiding them?

402
00:30:06,840 --> 00:30:08,280
Come this way.

403
00:30:08,360 --> 00:30:09,480
Follow me.

404
00:30:19,600 --> 00:30:21,160
