412
00:31:05,480 --> 00:31:07,240
not a dog.

413
00:31:09,360 --> 00:31:10,720
So who is the dog here?

414
00:31:11,280 --> 00:31:13,280
It's me, of course.

415
00:31:25,160 --> 00:31:26,480
Not even a little.

416
00:31:27,480 --> 00:31:29,040
No sign of a smile at all.

417
00:31:30,280 --> 00:31:31,920
Why did you come to see me?

418
00:31:32,520 --> 00:31:34,160
I wanted to take you out.

419
00:31:34,640 --> 00:31:37,840
If you're not mad at me anymore,
please come with me.

420
00:31:38,480 --> 00:31:39,720
Take me out?

421
00:31:39,800 --> 00:31:42,080
You just got here. We will…

422
00:31:42,160 --> 00:31:45,640
I mean, Cheewa and I will show you around.

423
00:31:46,200 --> 00:31:47,840
Let's go. Come on.

424
00:32:07,760 --> 00:32:09,000
- Cheewa!
- My gosh!

425
00:32:09,080 --> 00:32:10,160
Cheewan.

426
00:32:11,280 --> 00:32:12,800
You scared the hell out of me.

427
00:32:17,000 --> 00:32:18,240
Cheewan,

428
00:32:18,320 --> 00:32:19,520
