429
00:32:24,040 --> 00:32:25,000
Look.

430
00:32:28,600 --> 00:32:30,640
It's nothing. Let's go.

431
00:32:31,200 --> 00:32:33,280
Saruj, hello.

432
00:32:33,360 --> 00:32:34,240
Hello.

433
00:32:34,840 --> 00:32:36,120
- Let's go.
- Let's go.

434
00:32:37,760 --> 00:32:39,920
Mr. Saruj, let's go.

435
00:32:40,000 --> 00:32:41,320
Let's go.

436
00:32:59,760 --> 00:33:01,080
Mr. Saruj,

437
00:33:01,160 --> 00:33:03,800
I want to look in this shop.

438
00:33:03,880 --> 00:33:05,440
This shop called…

439
00:33:05,520 --> 00:33:07,120
Ki…

440
00:33:07,200 --> 00:33:08,920
Kirchhofer.

441
00:33:09,880 --> 00:33:11,960
Yes, that's it. Let's go.

442
00:33:12,880 --> 00:33:13,960
Let's go.

443
00:33:19,240 --> 00:33:20,280
Thank you.

444
00:33:22,800 --> 00:33:24,400
Come on.

445
00:33:35,560 --> 00:33:38,400
I'll take a look
at the keychains over there.

446
00:33:38,960 --> 00:33:39,800
I'll come with you.

447
00:33:39,880 --> 00:33:42,680
No, you stay here.

448
00:33:42,760 --> 00:33:46,720
Mr. Saruj, please take care of Poncheewa.

449
00:33:46,800 --> 00:33:48,040
Sure.

450
00:34:09,960 --> 00:34:11,600
Why aren't they talking?

451
00:35:37,160 --> 00:35:38,280
Cheewa.

452
00:35:38,360 --> 00:35:39,360
Yes?

453
00:35:39,440 --> 00:35:41,400
Ask him about Switzerland.

454
00:35:42,080 --> 00:35:44,520
