496
00:38:19,200 --> 00:38:20,600
You wouldn't like a foreigner.

497
00:38:22,520 --> 00:38:25,000
You're not dating a foreigner, are you?

498
00:38:26,840 --> 00:38:27,920
No.

499
00:38:30,280 --> 00:38:33,960
That means you prefer Thai women, right?

500
00:38:34,520 --> 00:38:35,400
Well…

501
00:38:35,480 --> 00:38:37,000
