514
00:39:19,360 --> 00:39:20,440
Yes.

515
00:39:40,840 --> 00:39:42,560
That's it!

516
00:39:47,640 --> 00:39:49,280
What are you doing?

517
00:39:50,320 --> 00:39:53,040
What? What do you mean?

518
00:39:53,120 --> 00:39:57,080
