521
00:40:12,920 --> 00:40:14,400
Like this.

522
00:40:15,720 --> 00:40:16,640
My gosh.

523
00:41:04,200 --> 00:41:06,760
Since you came here to study

524
00:41:07,320 --> 00:41:09,720
and came to stay here with Cheewan,

525
00:41:10,880 --> 00:41:13,680
