00:41:46,560 --> 00:41:47,960
Be careful.

533
00:41:53,040 --> 00:41:54,400
Excuse me.

534
00:41:55,440 --> 00:41:56,560
Cheewa.

535
00:42:00,920 --> 00:42:02,080
Here is the rent.

536
00:42:02,960 --> 00:42:04,520
I'm sorry for paying you late.

537
00:42:04,600 --> 00:42:06,200
It's all right.

538
00:42:08,760 --> 00:42:11,200
My gosh.

539
00:42:11,280 --> 00:42:14,040
You gave her a rose.

540
00:42:14,600 --> 00:42:15,960
Where's mine?

541
00:42:16,840 --> 00:42:18,520
I only grew one,

542
00:42:18,600 --> 00:42:20,480
so there's only one rose.

543
00:42:21,800 --> 00:42:22,960
I see.

544
00:42:24,560 --> 00:42:27,840
By the way, have you heard the news?

545
00:42:27,920 --> 00:42:32,240
The new first secretary asked me
to book some accommodation for him.

546
00:42:32,320 --> 00:42:35,640
